and pull the heart out.

782
00:51:36,393 --> 00:51:37,961
You can't just…

783
00:51:38,028 --> 00:51:42,232
Right ventricle suture complete.
You're up.

784
00:51:42,299 --> 00:51:46,002
-Right ventricle suture complete.
