791
00:52:10,260 --> 00:52:11,728
I've got one ready.

792
00:52:19,636 --> 00:52:21,571
All right. Here we go.

793
00:52:21,638 --> 00:52:24,207
-We'll do anything we can!
-Right!

794
00:52:28,445 --> 00:52:29,412
Here.

795
00:52:39,055 --> 00:52:41,591
The heart is coming toward the Caesar.

796
00:52:41,658 --> 00:52:43,960
The heart won't stabilize like that.

797
00:52:44,027 --> 00:52:46,763
There's no arm to hold it like the Darwin.

798
00:52:49,065 --> 00:52:51,801
-I'll suture with one hand.
-With one hand?

799
00:52:55,505 --> 00:52:57,741
The left arm will hold the heart
and the right will suture.

800
00:52:58,375 --> 00:52:59,276
Got it.

801
00:53:00,510 --> 00:53:02,112
Almost at one hour.

802
00:53:02,179 --> 00:53:04,014
Come on… let's make it work!

803
00:53:04,080 --> 00:53:05,415
TIME LIMIT
4 MINUTES REMAINING

804
00:53:11,288 --> 00:53:12,722
He's using his right hand only.

