written independently by Tojo University.

876
00:59:46,749 --> 00:59:48,318
Apart from the paper itself,

877
00:59:49,185 --> 00:59:51,120
the video attached was great.

878
00:59:52,155 --> 00:59:55,592
<i>The Saeki Method executed</i>
<i>through remote operation of the Caesar.</i>

879
00:59:55,658 --> 00:59:56,626
MEDICAL ROBOT CAESAR PAPER

