881
01:00:01,497 --> 01:00:03,232
<i>using top-notch technology.</i>

882
01:00:04,334 --> 01:00:06,002
I won't stand for this!

883
01:00:06,069 --> 01:00:07,670
It's against the rules
of collaborative research!

884
01:00:07,737 --> 01:00:12,375
