will better benefit future patients.

885
01:00:13,443 --> 01:00:14,811
Thank you for your time.

886
01:00:15,478 --> 01:00:17,447
What… Hello?

887
01:00:28,591 --> 01:00:30,493
Takashina…

888
01:00:34,397 --> 01:00:36,566
<i>JAPAN SURGICAL JOURNAL</i>

889
01:00:37,200 --> 01:00:39,435
This is pretty good work.

890
01:00:41,070 --> 01:00:44,641
You put your life on the line
for this paper.

891
01:00:45,608 --> 01:00:48,011
It's all thanks to your cooperation.

892
01:00:48,611 --> 01:00:50,913
Was Dr. Tokai's use of the Caesar

893
01:00:51,447 --> 01:00:52,882
part of your plan as well?

894
01:00:55,585 --> 01:00:59,656
Dr. Tokai won't let me die just yet.

895
01:01:02,725 --> 01:01:03,660
Forgive me,

896
