information about the patient.

904
01:01:53,176 --> 01:01:54,010
Okay.

905
01:01:54,077 --> 01:01:54,977
All right.

906
01:01:55,678 --> 01:01:57,313
Please take care of him.

907
01:02:01,017 --> 01:02:03,753
