909
01:02:09,292 --> 01:02:12,762
I was once admitted here at Tojo.

910
01:02:14,130 --> 01:02:15,531
Is that so?

911
01:02:22,205 --> 01:02:25,308
TATSUJI IINUMA

912
01:02:31,247 --> 01:02:32,682
I told you, didn't I?

913
01:02:34,383 --> 01:02:36,819
There's only one man in this world

